OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FChief medic told staff to  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fdelete WhatsApps every day 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's chief medical officer told  
OL,6, colleagues to delete WhatsApp messages 
OL,7, "every day" during the pandemic, the UK
OL,8, Covid Inquiry had heard.               
OL,10,FProf Gregor Smith said he erased his   
OL,11,Fown messages "on a frequent basis" in  
OL,12,Fline with government policy.           
OL,14,FHe said any "pertinent" information    
OL,15,Fabout "definitive" decision making was 
OL,16,Frecorded via email.                    
OL,18,FThe Scottish government has said it is 
OL,19,Fsatisfied "all steps are being taken to
OL,20,Fmeet the inquiry's requests".          
